1
00:00:09,926 --> 00:00:13,138
DISEMBER 2020

2
00:00:14,556 --> 00:00:16,933
PUSAT TINJU JINNAM

3
00:01:27,128 --> 00:01:28,463
Encik, tunggu.

4
00:01:28,546 --> 00:01:30,048
Perlu pakai pelitup muka.

5
00:01:30,131 --> 00:01:31,257
Okey. Jalanlah.

6
00:01:31,341 --> 00:01:33,635
Dalam bas wajib guna pelitup muka.

7
00:01:33,718 --> 00:01:34,594
Jalan sahajalah.

8
00:01:34,677 --> 00:01:36,638
Turun dan pakai pelitup dulu.

9
00:01:36,721 --> 00:01:38,473
Apa hal mengarah orang?

10
00:01:38,556 --> 00:01:41,601
- Kami akan didenda…
- Suka hati sayalah!

11
00:01:41,684 --> 00:01:44,229
- Siapa awak nak mengarah saya?
- Encik.

12
00:01:44,312 --> 00:01:47,190
Tugas awak memandu bas. Buatlah kerja!

13
00:01:47,273 --> 00:01:48,108
Cis!

14
00:01:48,191 --> 00:01:50,443
Tolong pakai pelitup muka dulu.

15
00:01:50,527 --> 00:01:52,070
- Jahanam!
- Jangan begini.

16
00:01:52,153 --> 00:01:54,781
- Penumpang lain menunggu.
- Lepas! Apa ini?

17
00:01:54,864 --> 00:01:56,574
- Lepas, tak guna!
- Alamak!

18
00:01:56,658 --> 00:01:58,785
- Lepas!
- Maafkan saya.

19
00:01:58,868 --> 00:02:00,453
Apa hal? Kau siapa?

20
00:02:00,537 --> 00:02:01,371
Maafkan saya.

21
00:02:01,454 --> 00:02:02,997
Encik patut jalan kaki. Maaf.

22
00:02:03,081 --> 00:02:05,208
- Tak guna!
- Saya minta maaf.

23
00:02:06,209 --> 00:02:07,335
Hei, tak guna!

24
00:02:07,418 --> 00:02:08,628
- Maaf.
- Hei!

25
00:02:09,295 --> 00:02:10,296
Maaf.

26
00:02:11,297 --> 00:02:12,841
Aduhai. Maafkan saya.

27
00:02:12,924 --> 00:02:14,467
Berhati-hati. Maaf!

28
00:02:14,551 --> 00:02:16,094
Cis!

29
00:02:17,762 --> 00:02:19,347
Ceh.

30
00:02:20,348 --> 00:02:22,475
- Maaf.
- Tak guna betul.

31
00:02:24,811 --> 00:02:25,770
Maaf.

32
00:02:25,854 --> 00:02:27,021
Berambuslah.

33
00:02:29,691 --> 00:02:30,525
Aduh.

34
00:02:31,192 --> 00:02:33,194
Aduhai, maaflah.

35
00:02:33,278 --> 00:02:34,904
- Terima kasih.
- Sama-sama.

36
00:02:37,031 --> 00:02:38,658
Terima kasih banyak.

37
00:02:38,741 --> 00:02:39,909
- Hebat.
- Terima kasih.

38
00:03:21,951 --> 00:03:23,578
Saya minta maaf.

39
00:03:24,162 --> 00:03:26,873
Tak sangka ia akan berpanjangan.

40
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:32,086
Maaf kerana menyusahkan awak.

41
00:03:32,170 --> 00:03:34,756
Saya akan buat sesuatu untuk bulan depan.

42
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:39,928
Jadi, boleh beri saya masa sebulan lagi?

43
00:03:41,262 --> 00:03:42,972
Saya pasti akan bayar semula.

44
00:03:43,806 --> 00:03:46,726
Ya, saya akan usahakan sesuatu.

45
00:03:46,809 --> 00:03:48,561
Okey, terima kasih.

46
00:04:27,016 --> 00:04:30,895
BLOODHOUNDS

47
00:04:34,065 --> 00:04:37,026
Dalam kemelesetan ekonomi akibat COVID-19,

48
00:04:37,110 --> 00:04:38,903
sebuah projek terbengkalai

49
00:04:38,987 --> 00:04:41,072
mengancam keselamatan orang ramai.

50
00:04:41,155 --> 00:04:44,659
Pembinaan bangunan di belakang ini
telah tertangguh dua kali

51
00:04:44,742 --> 00:04:46,786
akibat jangkitan COVID-19.

52
00:04:46,869 --> 00:04:49,580
Syarikat pembinaan dilaporkan muflis,

53
00:04:49,664 --> 00:04:52,292
membiarkan bangunan terbengkalai
selama empat bulan.

54
00:04:52,375 --> 00:04:54,335
Kerajaan negeri perlu mengambil tindakan.

55
00:05:02,051 --> 00:05:05,179
Di Amerika, lebih 3.5 juta
pekerja hotel diberhentikan

56
00:05:05,263 --> 00:05:06,681
dalam suku ketiga.

57
00:05:06,764 --> 00:05:09,017
Maksud saya, tiada syarikat asing

58
00:05:09,100 --> 00:05:12,228
akan berminat dengan hotel ini
dalam masa tiga, empat tahun ini.

59
00:05:12,729 --> 00:05:14,439
Inikan pula syarikat tempatan.

60
00:05:14,522 --> 00:05:15,857
Awak sangat yakin.

61
00:05:15,940 --> 00:05:19,652
Kawan-kawan saya bakal mengetuai
syarikat-syarikat utama negara.

62
00:05:19,736 --> 00:05:22,739
Inilah kesimpulan hasil
perbincangan panjang kami

63
00:05:22,822 --> 00:05:24,240
dan boleh dianggap benar.

64
00:05:25,325 --> 00:05:28,536
Sebenarnya, inilah kenyataannya.

65
00:05:29,287 --> 00:05:31,581
Eloklah awak berunding dengan saya.

66
00:05:32,081 --> 00:05:32,915
Pengarah Hong.

67
00:05:34,083 --> 00:05:37,295
Bangunan ini berhutang
400 bilion dengan bank kami.

68
00:05:37,795 --> 00:05:40,131
Jumlah 300 bilion bukannya rundingan.

69
00:05:40,214 --> 00:05:41,632
Dalam situasi sekarang,

70
00:05:41,716 --> 00:05:43,176
bukankah lebih baik rugi kecil?

71
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:45,053
Bagaimana nak berurus niaga?

72
00:05:45,636 --> 00:05:48,723
Saya bukan ahli perniagaan
tapi pemilik bank.

73
00:05:49,307 --> 00:05:51,392
Tuan-tuan berdua.

74
00:05:52,018 --> 00:05:53,811
Saya adakan pertemuan ini…

75
00:05:53,895 --> 00:05:56,189
- Ya.
- …kerana datuk bandar berharap

76
00:05:56,272 --> 00:05:59,400
agar projek disudahkan segera
demi keselamatan orang ramai.

77
00:05:59,484 --> 00:06:01,361
Perlulah ada perbincangan.

78
00:06:01,444 --> 00:06:04,697
Maksud awak, saya tak boleh
dibawa berunding?

79
00:06:04,781 --> 00:06:06,699
Ini bukan rundingan.

80
00:06:15,625 --> 00:06:17,293
Maaf saya lewat.

81
00:06:18,544 --> 00:06:21,756
Ini En. Kim Myeong-gil
yang saya sebut tadi.

82
00:06:22,256 --> 00:06:23,257
Sila berkenalan.

83
00:06:23,341 --> 00:06:26,928
Dia diperkenalkan
oleh Ahli Dewan Seo Woo-hyeon yang juga

84
00:06:27,011 --> 00:06:28,179
teman datuk bandar.

85
00:06:29,347 --> 00:06:30,598
Saya Kim Myeong-gil.

86
00:06:32,767 --> 00:06:34,852
KIM MYEONG-GIL

87
00:06:35,937 --> 00:06:37,814
Kita berhubung kemudian.

88
00:06:38,439 --> 00:06:39,273
Baiklah.

89
00:06:44,028 --> 00:06:44,946
Saya Kim Myeong-gil.

90
00:06:55,706 --> 00:06:58,126
Maaf, tapi apa bidang awak?

91
00:06:59,127 --> 00:07:00,878
Kebanyakannya pelaburan.

92
00:07:00,962 --> 00:07:05,258
Saya turut tawarkan bantuan sebaik mungkin
kepada mereka yang memerlukan.

93
00:07:05,758 --> 00:07:07,635
Awak ceti?

94
00:07:09,095 --> 00:07:12,223
Apa ini? Awak jemput lintah darat?

95
00:07:13,141 --> 00:07:15,476
Bukan itu sahaja bidang dia.

96
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:18,020
Ini bukan tempat untuk lintah darat.

97
00:07:20,398 --> 00:07:23,109
Awak anak sulung
Pengerusi Hong Woo-geun, bukan?

98
00:07:24,318 --> 00:07:27,447
Saya pernah bekerja
dengan Pengerusi Bang dari Myeongdong.

99
00:07:27,530 --> 00:07:30,658
Tentu awak tak ingat
sebab waktu itu awak masih kecil,

100
00:07:30,741 --> 00:07:32,201
tapi ketika IMF melanda,

101
00:07:32,869 --> 00:07:35,872
Kumpulan Iil dengan sejarah 50 tahun
hampir muflis

102
00:07:35,955 --> 00:07:37,415
kerana enam bilion won.

103
00:07:37,957 --> 00:07:43,045
Pengerusi Hong bertemu bos saya,
Pengerusi Bang, untuk dapatkan bantuan.

104
00:07:43,546 --> 00:07:47,133
Sambil melutut dia merayu
untuk selamatkan syarikat dia.

105
00:07:47,633 --> 00:07:49,427
Kesungguhan dan keikhlasan dia

106
00:07:49,927 --> 00:07:51,762
menyentuh hati Pengerusi Bang.

107
00:07:53,097 --> 00:07:57,852
Saya pergi ke rumah awak dengan beg berisi
wang tunai berjumlah enam bilion.

108
00:07:58,644 --> 00:08:02,690
Ibu awak hidangkan tembikai tempatan
sebagai tanda terima kasih.

109
00:08:02,773 --> 00:08:03,733
Saya ingat lagi.

110
00:08:05,276 --> 00:08:08,070
Duit tak kotor.
Bezanya pada cara ia digunakan.

111
00:08:08,154 --> 00:08:10,740
Jika digunakan untuk kebaikan, baiklah ia.

112
00:08:11,324 --> 00:08:14,202
Saya datang dengan niat untuk membantu.

113
00:08:17,955 --> 00:08:20,458
Sejauh mana perbincangan tadi?

114
00:08:21,125 --> 00:08:23,461
Jumlah yang dirundingkan agak berbeza.

115
00:08:23,961 --> 00:08:24,837
Itu isunya.

116
00:08:24,921 --> 00:08:27,215
Begitu. Boleh saya tahu berapa?

117
00:08:27,298 --> 00:08:28,466
Seratus bilion won.

118
00:08:33,054 --> 00:08:34,263
Awak bercadang

119
00:08:35,097 --> 00:08:36,474
untuk uruskan sendiri?

120
00:08:37,099 --> 00:08:39,519
Graduan pengurusan hotel di Switzerland,

121
00:08:40,019 --> 00:08:41,437
bekerja 4 tahun di Hong Kong.

122
00:08:41,521 --> 00:08:43,648
Nampaknya, awak dah bersedia.

123
00:08:45,316 --> 00:08:48,444
Jika awak tak keberatan,
boleh saya jadi pelabur?

124
00:08:50,404 --> 00:08:51,239
Berapa?

125
00:08:51,322 --> 00:08:52,156
Itu…

126
00:08:52,865 --> 00:08:55,785
Saya akan melabur 100 bilion won.

127
00:08:59,830 --> 00:09:01,707
Jika tak cukup, saya tambah.

128
00:09:02,208 --> 00:09:03,167
Apa syaratnya?

129
00:09:03,751 --> 00:09:05,503
Ada tiga syarat.

130
00:09:06,504 --> 00:09:07,338
Pertama,

131
00:09:07,838 --> 00:09:09,840
bina sebuah kasino kecil

132
00:09:09,924 --> 00:09:12,176
di tingkat teratas hotel.

133
00:09:12,260 --> 00:09:14,804
Seperti impian awak untuk mengurus hotel,

134
00:09:14,887 --> 00:09:17,431
saya berimpian
untuk memiliki sebuah kasino.

135
00:09:18,432 --> 00:09:21,769
Kedua, saya perlu bantuan awak
untuk pembukaan sebuah bar

136
00:09:21,852 --> 00:09:23,563
di tingkat bawah tanah hotel.

137
00:09:23,646 --> 00:09:24,897
Akhir sekali,

138
00:09:25,398 --> 00:09:27,358
jika wabak penyakit melanda,

139
00:09:27,441 --> 00:09:30,820
saya mahu hotel ini dijadikan
ruang kuarantin percuma

140
00:09:30,903 --> 00:09:33,406
bagi golongan yang kurang berkemampuan.

141
00:09:34,490 --> 00:09:38,077
Dalam tempoh sukar ini,
kita patut saling membantu.

142
00:09:38,578 --> 00:09:39,453
Barulah

143
00:09:40,413 --> 00:09:41,747
dunia ini lebih baik.

144
00:09:46,043 --> 00:09:47,503
Saya bersedia

145
00:09:48,546 --> 00:09:50,715
untuk membuat pelaburan seawal esok.

146
00:10:07,607 --> 00:10:08,441
Berjaya?

147
00:10:09,984 --> 00:10:11,819
- Ya.
- Mereka akan terima?

148
00:10:12,987 --> 00:10:15,740
- Ya.
- Okey!

149
00:10:16,407 --> 00:10:17,283
Bagus!

150
00:10:17,366 --> 00:10:20,286
Sekarang saya boleh fokus
pada hiasan dalaman bar.

151
00:10:20,369 --> 00:10:24,540
Hei, orang tak peduli tentang hiasan.
Yang penting, pelayan wanita.

152
00:10:24,624 --> 00:10:26,459
Cari pelayan-pelayan cantik.

153
00:10:27,043 --> 00:10:29,128
Buat sahaja kerja awak, celaka.

154
00:10:29,712 --> 00:10:32,214
Awak cantik tapi mulut celopar.

155
00:10:32,298 --> 00:10:34,884
Apa hal awak mengata saya, jahanam?

156
00:10:37,637 --> 00:10:39,013
Pengelap muka.

157
00:10:39,597 --> 00:10:40,431
Oh, ya.

158
00:10:43,392 --> 00:10:44,226
Nah.

159
00:10:59,742 --> 00:11:00,785
Jom.

160
00:11:05,206 --> 00:11:06,290
Bangunan Seongeun?

161
00:11:06,791 --> 00:11:10,002
Tiada penyewa yang ada
kaitan dengan polis atau pendakwa.

162
00:11:10,086 --> 00:11:11,379
Termasuk biras?

163
00:11:11,462 --> 00:11:14,340
Saya terlepas pandang sekali itu sahaja.

164
00:11:14,423 --> 00:11:16,217
Periksa juga kekasih mereka.

165
00:11:16,717 --> 00:11:18,552
Periksa agar dia tak risau.

166
00:11:18,636 --> 00:11:20,930
Awak patut jaga tepi kain awak.

167
00:11:21,013 --> 00:11:22,098
Jang-do.

168
00:11:23,265 --> 00:11:25,601
Jaga bahasa dengan kakak ipar awak.

169
00:11:27,019 --> 00:11:28,104
Saya minta maaf.

170
00:11:28,187 --> 00:11:30,606
Minta maaf dengan saya, dungu!

171
00:11:31,524 --> 00:11:33,734
Si dungu ini minta maaf, cik.

172
00:11:33,818 --> 00:11:36,487
Cepatlah. Saya haus arak.

173
00:11:36,570 --> 00:11:37,405
Baiklah.

174
00:11:40,491 --> 00:11:43,536
Kejohanan Petinju Muda KBFC 2020.

175
00:11:43,619 --> 00:11:48,290
Biasanya, arena ini dipenuhi dengan
sorakan peminat, tapi kerana COVID-19,

176
00:11:48,374 --> 00:11:52,378
lokasi ini kosong
dan suasana terasa agak suram.

177
00:11:52,461 --> 00:11:54,797
Betul. Kejohanan begini biasanya

178
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:57,883
diiringi dengan sorakan,
tapi hari ini sunyi.

179
00:11:57,967 --> 00:11:59,427
Kita mulakan dengan

180
00:11:59,510 --> 00:12:01,303
perlawanan pusingan ketiga Hong.

181
00:12:01,387 --> 00:12:02,972
Ini perlawanan middleweight.

182
00:12:03,055 --> 00:12:04,598
Hong Woo-jin berseluar merah,

183
00:12:04,682 --> 00:12:06,684
dan Jung Jae-hun berseluar biru.

184
00:12:06,767 --> 00:12:07,601
Serang.

185
00:12:07,685 --> 00:12:09,562
- Serangan hebat.
- Betul.

186
00:12:09,645 --> 00:12:10,980
Hong bersandar pada tali.

187
00:12:11,063 --> 00:12:13,733
Dia sengaja menjengkelkan lawan dia.

188
00:12:13,816 --> 00:12:16,277
Betul. Dia nampak tenang.

189
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:17,903
- "Cubalah jika boleh."
- Ya.

190
00:12:17,987 --> 00:12:19,321
"Awak boleh kalau…"

191
00:12:19,405 --> 00:12:20,239
Tumbukan utama!

192
00:12:20,322 --> 00:12:21,157
Bagus!

193
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:22,450
Serangan cantik.

194
00:12:22,533 --> 00:12:24,285
Kini tumbukan di muka!

195
00:12:24,368 --> 00:12:26,537
Lawan dia rebah! Hong Woo-jin!

196
00:12:26,620 --> 00:12:29,039
Serangan kembar dan kombo satu-dua.

197
00:12:29,123 --> 00:12:31,959
Ya, lihat gerak kaki dia.
Dia pandai menghibur.

198
00:12:32,042 --> 00:12:33,294
Wah, KO.

199
00:12:33,836 --> 00:12:35,463
Seterusnya, kita saksikan

200
00:12:35,546 --> 00:12:37,465
aksi Kim Gun-woo dan Kim Rae-hyeon.

201
00:12:37,548 --> 00:12:39,550
Petinju baru Kim Gun-woo berseluar biru.

202
00:12:39,633 --> 00:12:42,511
Kim mencari peluang dalam pertahanan.

203
00:12:42,595 --> 00:12:43,512
Hebat!

204
00:12:43,596 --> 00:12:45,556
- Tumbukan utama!
- Dia jatuh melutut!

205
00:12:45,639 --> 00:12:48,142
Betul. Tumbukan tepat di hulu hati…

206
00:12:48,225 --> 00:12:50,186
- Perlawanan tamat.
- Betul.

207
00:12:50,269 --> 00:12:52,480
Tamat dengan satu tumbukan.

208
00:12:52,563 --> 00:12:54,440
Semua lawan tewas dengan satu tumbukan.

209
00:12:54,523 --> 00:12:56,150
- Dia tiada cacat cela.
- Bagus.

210
00:12:56,233 --> 00:12:58,068
Petinju baru yang menggerunkan.

211
00:12:58,652 --> 00:13:00,446
Perlawanan semakin sengit.

212
00:13:00,529 --> 00:13:01,989
- Dia tersepit.
- Betul.

213
00:13:05,326 --> 00:13:08,245
Dia humban lawan. Dia tolak lawan dia.

214
00:13:08,329 --> 00:13:09,872
Itu faul.

215
00:13:09,955 --> 00:13:11,081
- Betul.
- Dia mulakan.

216
00:13:11,165 --> 00:13:13,375
- Dia terlalu mengikut perasaan.
- Betul.

217
00:13:13,459 --> 00:13:15,044
- Mula!
- Ayuh!

218
00:13:15,544 --> 00:13:18,297
Dia selak rambut.
Kemahiran persembahan hebat.

219
00:13:18,380 --> 00:13:20,257
- Betul.
- Menjengkelkan lawan.

220
00:13:20,341 --> 00:13:21,342
Dia mengelak.

221
00:13:21,967 --> 00:13:23,260
Lihat dia mengelak!

222
00:13:25,763 --> 00:13:27,807
Sekali lagi… Dia berjaya! KO!

223
00:13:27,890 --> 00:13:29,850
Inilah kemahiran Hong Woo-jin.

224
00:13:29,934 --> 00:13:32,144
- Betul.
- Dua tumbukan pantas dan lurus!

225
00:13:32,228 --> 00:13:33,979
Hong Woo-jin, budak marin.

226
00:13:34,063 --> 00:13:36,398
Hong mara ke pusingan seterusnya.

227
00:13:37,441 --> 00:13:39,860
Kini, perlawanan antara Kim dan Lee.

228
00:13:41,821 --> 00:13:43,614
Kim seorang yang sasa.

229
00:13:43,697 --> 00:13:44,782
Betul.

230
00:13:44,865 --> 00:13:45,783
Dia mengelak.

231
00:13:45,866 --> 00:13:48,452
- Kim pakar serangan jarak dekat.
- Ya.

232
00:13:48,536 --> 00:13:51,372
Dia menggunakan kemahiran dia dengan baik.

233
00:13:51,455 --> 00:13:53,541
Satu lagi tumbukan, dia mengelak.

234
00:13:53,624 --> 00:13:54,667
Tumbukan abdomen!

235
00:13:55,376 --> 00:13:56,836
Tewas dengan satu tumbukan lagi!

236
00:13:56,919 --> 00:13:58,170
Tumbukan kiri.

237
00:13:58,254 --> 00:13:59,088
Betul.

238
00:13:59,171 --> 00:14:01,382
Dulu saya memiliki bakat yang sama.

239
00:14:01,465 --> 00:14:03,551
- Awak okey?
- Ya.

240
00:14:03,634 --> 00:14:04,760
Sebab itu awak menang.

241
00:14:04,844 --> 00:14:06,053
Betul.

242
00:14:06,846 --> 00:14:08,514
Kim Gun-woo dan Hong Woo-jin.

243
00:14:08,597 --> 00:14:11,267
- Betul.
- Kita nantikan pemenang kita.

244
00:14:11,350 --> 00:14:12,726
Kawal gerakan.

245
00:14:12,810 --> 00:14:13,769
Jangan hayun.

246
00:14:13,853 --> 00:14:14,937
Hati-hati.

247
00:14:15,521 --> 00:14:16,856
Tumbukan kiri dia hebat.

248
00:14:23,737 --> 00:14:26,240
Hei, saya tentera marin.

249
00:14:27,116 --> 00:14:28,492
Elak tumbukan kiri.

250
00:14:28,576 --> 00:14:30,911
Saya tentera marin kebal. Kebal!

251
00:14:30,995 --> 00:14:34,081
Jangan menangis jika dibelasah.
Saya akan bunuh awak.

252
00:14:39,044 --> 00:14:40,254
- Ayuh!
- Ayuh!

253
00:14:43,632 --> 00:14:45,801
Selamat berjaya. Ke sudut masing-masing.

254
00:14:50,055 --> 00:14:51,891
Setakat ini prestasi dia hebat.

255
00:14:51,974 --> 00:14:55,686
Petinju baru, Kim Gun-woo,
memiliki gaya tinju yang berbeza.

256
00:14:55,769 --> 00:14:59,440
Betul. Kim menewaskan lawan
dengan serangan jarak dekat.

257
00:14:59,523 --> 00:15:01,567
- Betul.
- Sementara itu,

258
00:15:01,650 --> 00:15:06,322
Hong peninju jarak jauh
dengan serangan licik.

259
00:15:06,405 --> 00:15:09,116
Ya, Hong Woo-jin tahu berseronok
dalam perlawanannya.

260
00:15:09,199 --> 00:15:10,034
Betul.

261
00:15:10,117 --> 00:15:13,037
Dengan lawan yang lurus bendul.

262
00:15:13,120 --> 00:15:15,831
Dia dah bertindak! Dia merapatkan jarak!

263
00:15:15,915 --> 00:15:18,500
Mampukah Hong mengelak? Berjayakah?

264
00:15:18,584 --> 00:15:19,960
Dia berjaya mengelak.

265
00:15:20,044 --> 00:15:24,131
- Ya, Hong sangat pantas.
- Betul.

266
00:15:24,214 --> 00:15:26,425
Kim juga petinju middleweight…

267
00:15:26,508 --> 00:15:28,594
Dia membuat hayunan!

268
00:15:29,762 --> 00:15:31,055
- Ya.
- Dia halang.

269
00:15:31,138 --> 00:15:33,015
Pertahanan yang bagus oleh Kim.

270
00:15:33,098 --> 00:15:35,351
- Betul.
- Dia seperti batu.

271
00:15:35,434 --> 00:15:37,770
Dia penuh berjaga-jaga.

272
00:15:37,853 --> 00:15:38,687
Tumbuk sungkit.

273
00:15:38,771 --> 00:15:40,481
- Itu dia.
- Dia berjaya.

274
00:15:40,564 --> 00:15:42,191
Tepat sekali.

275
00:15:42,274 --> 00:15:43,484
Persembahan menarik.

276
00:15:43,567 --> 00:15:44,693
Tumbukan kanan!

277
00:15:44,777 --> 00:15:46,862
Kini giliran Hong.

278
00:15:46,946 --> 00:15:50,074
Hong membuat serangan bertubi.

279
00:15:50,908 --> 00:15:52,201
Satu lagi tumbukan kiri!

280
00:15:52,284 --> 00:15:53,827
Bolehkah dia bertahan?

281
00:15:53,911 --> 00:15:55,996
- Dia rebah.
- Rebah!

282
00:15:56,080 --> 00:15:57,623
- Dia rebah.
- Dua…

283
00:15:57,706 --> 00:16:01,085
Ya, serangan abdomen
menyebabkan kejutan serta-merta.

284
00:16:01,168 --> 00:16:03,712
- Betul.
- Dalam masa lima saat sahaja.

285
00:16:03,796 --> 00:16:04,797
Woo-jin!

286
00:16:04,880 --> 00:16:06,340
Enam, tujuh…

287
00:16:06,423 --> 00:16:07,800
- Dia dah bangun.
- Betul.

288
00:16:07,883 --> 00:16:09,802
- Dia bertahan dengan baik.
- Betul…

289
00:16:09,885 --> 00:16:10,803
Betul.

290
00:16:10,886 --> 00:16:12,930
Tapi ia pasti menyakitkan.

291
00:16:13,013 --> 00:16:15,307
- Pasti ada kesan sampingan.
- Betul.

292
00:16:17,226 --> 00:16:18,060
Seranglah.

293
00:16:20,145 --> 00:16:22,606
Seranglah!

294
00:16:48,173 --> 00:16:49,008
Seranglah.

295
00:16:49,800 --> 00:16:52,052
Hei, seranglah.

296
00:16:54,221 --> 00:16:55,472
Jahanam.

297
00:16:57,891 --> 00:16:59,893
Seranglah!

298
00:17:01,812 --> 00:17:03,105
Adakah dia akan terpedaya?

299
00:17:03,188 --> 00:17:05,357
- Kim perlu berwaspada.
- Cepat!

300
00:17:05,441 --> 00:17:07,735
Dia dah bertindak! Berjayakah?

301
00:17:07,818 --> 00:17:11,155
Berhenti! Satu, dua…

302
00:17:11,238 --> 00:17:13,574
Tentu kecederaan agak serius.

303
00:17:13,657 --> 00:17:15,409
- Taktik dia memakan diri.
- KO.

304
00:17:15,492 --> 00:17:16,410
Betul.

305
00:17:16,493 --> 00:17:18,412
Kim menyerang

306
00:17:18,495 --> 00:17:24,293
dan menamatkan perlawanan
dengan teknik yang sama sekali lagi.

307
00:17:28,464 --> 00:17:29,590
Awak okey?

308
00:17:30,257 --> 00:17:32,843
Saya dah burukkan nama Tentera Marin.

309
00:17:33,552 --> 00:17:35,095
Tumbukan di hati memang sakit.

310
00:17:36,722 --> 00:17:37,639
Saya balik.

311
00:17:38,640 --> 00:17:39,475
Tak nak makan?

312
00:17:40,684 --> 00:17:41,810
Sekarang pandemik.

313
00:17:42,394 --> 00:17:45,564
Saya kena belasah.
Setidaknya, kita makan dulu.

314
00:18:01,455 --> 00:18:02,915
Buat pesanan ke rumah.

315
00:18:06,126 --> 00:18:06,960
Jumpa lagi.

316
00:18:23,227 --> 00:18:24,853
Apa hal? Kenapa? Apa?

317
00:18:25,854 --> 00:18:26,855
Nak pergi makan?

318
00:18:27,606 --> 00:18:29,274
Apa hal nak makan bersama?

319
00:18:29,858 --> 00:18:32,277
Saya ajak sebab nak makan samgyeopsal.

320
00:18:35,531 --> 00:18:36,573
Awak kasihankan saya?

321
00:18:37,157 --> 00:18:37,991
Tak.

322
00:18:38,075 --> 00:18:40,202
Pergi ajak petinju lain
yang awak tewaskan.

323
00:18:40,285 --> 00:18:41,912
Mereka dah balik.

324
00:18:43,122 --> 00:18:44,248
Cis.

325
00:18:56,760 --> 00:18:58,387
Awak menang sepuluh juta won?

326
00:18:58,470 --> 00:18:59,304
Ya.

327
00:19:00,264 --> 00:19:03,392
Kenapa makan samgyeopsal?
Jom makan mata rusuk.

328
00:19:03,475 --> 00:19:06,145
- Saya nak belanja 50,000 won sahaja.
- Kenapa?

329
00:19:06,228 --> 00:19:07,563
Selebihnya untuk mak saya.

330
00:19:08,147 --> 00:19:10,107
- Awak berhutang dengan dia?
- Tak.

331
00:19:10,190 --> 00:19:11,066
Jadi?

332
00:19:11,567 --> 00:19:13,402
Saya perlu bayar sewa kafe.

333
00:19:14,361 --> 00:19:15,195
Anak yang baik.

334
00:19:16,280 --> 00:19:17,614
Tambah 10,000 won.

335
00:19:17,698 --> 00:19:20,242
Ada bufet barbeku, 29,000 seorang.

336
00:19:20,325 --> 00:19:21,743
Daging lembu tempatan.

337
00:19:21,827 --> 00:19:22,911
Yakah? Di mana?

338
00:19:22,995 --> 00:19:24,079
Saya tipu, dungu.

339
00:19:25,622 --> 00:19:27,666
Mustahil daging tempatan semurah itu.

340
00:19:28,542 --> 00:19:30,127
Awak cuma tahu bertinju?

341
00:19:31,545 --> 00:19:33,881
Bufet itu okey. Tambah 10,000 sahaja.

342
00:19:33,964 --> 00:19:34,798
Tak nak.

343
00:19:37,301 --> 00:19:38,135
Hei.

344
00:19:48,061 --> 00:19:48,896
Jom.

345
00:19:50,564 --> 00:19:51,899
Kenapa tumbukan awak kuat?

346
00:19:52,482 --> 00:19:54,067
Ketika bekerja di medan sekerap

347
00:19:54,151 --> 00:19:56,028
saya berlatih dengan gunakan tayar.

348
00:19:56,111 --> 00:19:57,279
Tumbukan kiri sahaja?

349
00:19:58,530 --> 00:19:59,781
Kenapa kiri sahaja?

350
00:19:59,865 --> 00:20:01,867
Saya tanya awak latih tangan kiri sahaja.

351
00:20:01,950 --> 00:20:03,785
Saya latih kedua-duanya.

352
00:20:03,869 --> 00:20:05,537
Kenapa tangan kiri kuat sangat?

353
00:20:05,621 --> 00:20:07,456
Tangan kanan saya lebih kuat.

354
00:20:07,539 --> 00:20:08,874
Kenapa guna kiri?

355
00:20:09,458 --> 00:20:11,293
Saya tak sempat guna kanan.

356
00:20:12,669 --> 00:20:13,545
Berlagak.

357
00:20:14,588 --> 00:20:15,422
Kenapa?

358
00:20:15,505 --> 00:20:17,674
Lawan awak tak kuat
untuk tangan kanan awak.

359
00:20:18,258 --> 00:20:19,468
Hari ini, ya.

360
00:20:19,551 --> 00:20:21,386
Tengok? Berlagak betul.

361
00:20:21,970 --> 00:20:23,388
Tak, saya tak berlagak.

362
00:20:23,472 --> 00:20:24,306
Terbalikkan.

363
00:20:24,389 --> 00:20:26,308
Tak, tunggu 30 saat lagi.

364
00:20:26,391 --> 00:20:28,143
Boleh terbalikkan sekarang.

365
00:20:28,227 --> 00:20:31,355
Tak boleh.
Saya pernah bekerja di kedai barbeku.

366
00:20:31,438 --> 00:20:33,398
Banyak betul kerja sambilan awak.

367
00:20:34,107 --> 00:20:37,069
- Awak miskin?
- Ya, keluarga saya muflis.

368
00:20:39,488 --> 00:20:40,405
Apa berlaku?

369
00:20:42,950 --> 00:20:45,327
Ayah saya penyelidik di syarikat besar.

370
00:20:45,410 --> 00:20:47,871
Dia saman sebab dipecat,
tapi kalah lepas empat tahun.

371
00:20:48,997 --> 00:20:51,250
Semua kos kes bertukar jadi hutang.

372
00:20:52,334 --> 00:20:54,753
Syarikat besar bukan lawan kita.

373
00:20:54,836 --> 00:20:55,879
Betul.

374
00:20:58,674 --> 00:20:59,591
Apa kerja lain?

375
00:20:59,675 --> 00:21:03,553
Bermacam-macam, tapi biasanya
penghantaran dengan mak saya.

376
00:21:04,888 --> 00:21:06,265
Awak jaguh rupanya.

377
00:21:10,602 --> 00:21:12,980
Awak berkebolehan
dan tak sia-siakan hidup.

378
00:21:13,563 --> 00:21:15,107
Awak guna tangan kanan.

379
00:21:16,233 --> 00:21:17,567
Sejak bila awak bertinju?

380
00:21:18,277 --> 00:21:20,195
Sejak tiga tahun lalu.

381
00:21:20,279 --> 00:21:22,281
- Bila?
- Selepas khidmat negara.

382
00:21:22,364 --> 00:21:23,198
Begitu…

383
00:21:24,032 --> 00:21:26,243
Saya mula sejak dari gred enam.

384
00:21:26,326 --> 00:21:27,995
Ayah saya petinju kebangsaan.

385
00:21:28,078 --> 00:21:29,621
Hebatnya.

386
00:21:30,247 --> 00:21:31,540
Apa nama ayah awak?

387
00:21:31,623 --> 00:21:34,501
Hong Seong-geun.
Pemenang pingat gangsa Olimpik Barcelona.

388
00:21:34,584 --> 00:21:36,169
- Oh.
- Pernah dengar?

389
00:21:36,253 --> 00:21:37,379
Tak.

390
00:21:38,463 --> 00:21:40,048
Kebanyakan petinju kenal dia.

391
00:21:40,132 --> 00:21:42,134
Begitu. Maaf.

392
00:21:43,593 --> 00:21:45,429
Ayah awak yang ajar awak?

393
00:21:46,138 --> 00:21:47,264
Kami tak rapat.

394
00:21:48,140 --> 00:21:49,349
Kenapa?

395
00:21:49,433 --> 00:21:51,601
Ayah saya tak pernah
puas hati dengan saya.

396
00:21:52,102 --> 00:21:54,354
Dia menang pingat pada usia saya,

397
00:21:54,938 --> 00:21:56,565
jadi itu ukuran untuk saya.

398
00:21:59,651 --> 00:22:00,652
Jadi,

399
00:22:01,570 --> 00:22:04,948
ayah awak menangi pingat itu
pada usia 25 tahun?

400
00:22:06,074 --> 00:22:07,617
Taklah, 27 tahun.

401
00:22:10,746 --> 00:22:12,247
Berapa umur awak?

402
00:22:12,831 --> 00:22:14,041
Dua puluh tujuh.

403
00:22:14,624 --> 00:22:16,668
Saya minta maaf.

404
00:22:16,752 --> 00:22:18,879
Saya 25 tahun. Maafkan saya.

405
00:22:18,962 --> 00:22:20,756
Budak tak guna.

406
00:22:20,839 --> 00:22:21,673
Maaf.

407
00:22:21,757 --> 00:22:22,799
- Hei.
- Ya.

408
00:22:22,883 --> 00:22:24,593
Jaga kelakuan awak. Faham?

409
00:22:24,676 --> 00:22:25,886
- Baiklah.
- Faham?

410
00:22:26,720 --> 00:22:28,889
- Faham.
- Terbalikkan.

411
00:22:29,473 --> 00:22:31,266
Tak boleh. Seminit lagi.

412
00:22:31,350 --> 00:22:33,435
- Tak apa. Terbalikkan.
- Tak boleh.

413
00:22:33,518 --> 00:22:35,812
Ceh. Degil betul.

414
00:22:36,313 --> 00:22:37,147
Khidmat negara?

415
00:22:37,230 --> 00:22:40,192
Sudah, saya beritahu
saya bertinju selepas tamat…

416
00:22:40,275 --> 00:22:41,568
Saya tahu.

417
00:22:41,651 --> 00:22:43,987
Maksud saya, di mana awak ditugaskan?

418
00:22:44,071 --> 00:22:45,072
Itu pun tak faham.

419
00:22:45,155 --> 00:22:47,240
Saya bertugas dalam Tentera Marin.

420
00:22:48,450 --> 00:22:49,451
Hei!

421
00:22:50,035 --> 00:22:51,578
Saya tentera marin juga!

422
00:22:51,661 --> 00:22:52,579
Oh.

423
00:22:52,662 --> 00:22:53,914
Kelas berapa?

424
00:22:53,997 --> 00:22:56,041
Saya dari kelas 1,207.

425
00:22:58,293 --> 00:23:01,004
Tabik! Saya dari kelas 1,216, tuan!

426
00:23:01,088 --> 00:23:03,840
Apa awak buat ini? Duduklah.

427
00:23:03,924 --> 00:23:05,550
Sila terima tabik saya, tuan.

428
00:23:05,634 --> 00:23:06,885
Oh, ya…

429
00:23:10,472 --> 00:23:11,973
Pegawai Marin Kim.

430
00:23:12,057 --> 00:23:13,767
- Ya.
- Di mana awak bertugas?

431
00:23:14,393 --> 00:23:15,227
Divisyen Satu.

432
00:23:15,310 --> 00:23:17,229
Saya juga! Batalion mana?

433
00:23:18,438 --> 00:23:20,732
- Perisikan.
- Hebat.

434
00:23:21,400 --> 00:23:24,361
Itu hasrat saya juga, tapi saya gagal.

435
00:23:24,444 --> 00:23:27,072
- Oh.
- Perisikan kebanggaan tentera marin.

436
00:23:27,656 --> 00:23:29,324
Perisikan!

437
00:23:30,784 --> 00:23:33,453
Anggap kita kawan, tak perlu kaku sangat.

438
00:23:34,371 --> 00:23:35,205
Baiklah.

439
00:23:35,705 --> 00:23:36,998
Kita kawan.

440
00:23:37,082 --> 00:23:38,542
Baiklah, tuan.

441
00:23:38,625 --> 00:23:39,584
Hei.

442
00:23:41,044 --> 00:23:41,878
Nah.

443
00:23:45,048 --> 00:23:49,219
Hei, saya sangat bangga
jadi tentera marin.

444
00:23:49,302 --> 00:23:50,137
Kenapa?

445
00:23:50,220 --> 00:23:52,722
Dulu saya samseng di Incheon.

446
00:23:52,806 --> 00:23:55,725
Ketika bertugas, saya jumpa
ramai orang baik.

447
00:23:55,809 --> 00:23:56,935
Saya dah insaf.

448
00:23:57,018 --> 00:23:59,938
Kita berlatih
dan lalui kesukaran bersama-sama.

449
00:24:00,439 --> 00:24:01,523
Saya suka.

450
00:24:01,606 --> 00:24:02,774
Sedapnya.

451
00:24:02,858 --> 00:24:05,360
Kita bangun pagi, berlari, berpeluh

452
00:24:05,444 --> 00:24:06,987
mandi beramai-ramai

453
00:24:07,070 --> 00:24:08,697
sambil gosok belakang.

454
00:24:10,031 --> 00:24:11,283
Awak tak taasub, kan?

455
00:24:11,366 --> 00:24:12,451
Taklah.

456
00:24:12,534 --> 00:24:13,702
Cuba ini.

457
00:24:16,288 --> 00:24:17,247
Bagaimana?

458
00:24:19,583 --> 00:24:21,126
Rasa macam stik.

459
00:24:21,209 --> 00:24:22,043
Yakah?

460
00:24:23,670 --> 00:24:24,754
Hei, tengok ini.

461
00:24:26,006 --> 00:24:27,215
- Tiga ketul.
- Okey.

462
00:24:27,299 --> 00:24:29,259
- Letak ssamjang.
- Okey.

463
00:24:29,342 --> 00:24:30,677
Kimchi juga?

464
00:24:33,805 --> 00:24:34,973
Okey.

465
00:24:35,056 --> 00:24:37,017
- Pegawai Kim Gun-woo.
- Apa?

466
00:24:41,313 --> 00:24:42,481
- Sedap, kan?
- Ya.

467
00:24:43,607 --> 00:24:44,983
- Nak soju?
- Tak.

468
00:24:45,066 --> 00:24:46,943
- Kenapa? Sebab diet?
- Ya.

469
00:24:47,027 --> 00:24:49,237
Berdisiplin betul. Menyampah.

470
00:24:50,363 --> 00:24:52,616
Mak cik!

471
00:24:52,699 --> 00:24:55,744
Sebotol bir dan soju!

472
00:24:57,454 --> 00:24:59,080
Berapa harga kasut awak?

473
00:24:59,581 --> 00:25:01,124
- 1,200,000 won.
- Yakah?

474
00:25:02,042 --> 00:25:04,044
Mahalnya. Sama dengan sewa kedai.

475
00:25:04,127 --> 00:25:05,795
Kenapa mudah sangat percaya?

476
00:25:05,879 --> 00:25:07,297
Ini kasut tiruan.

477
00:25:09,049 --> 00:25:10,133
Nampak tulen.

478
00:25:10,217 --> 00:25:12,802
Bahagian depan kasut palsu berkilat.

479
00:25:12,886 --> 00:25:15,680
Kasut tulen gunakan sued.
Kemasan pun tak elok.

480
00:25:16,973 --> 00:25:19,434
Saya boleh carikan
yang lebih elok daripada tulen.

481
00:25:19,518 --> 00:25:21,853
- Yakah?
- Mengarut betul.

482
00:25:21,937 --> 00:25:25,106
Tiada yang boleh tandingi ketulenan.

483
00:25:26,233 --> 00:25:28,693
Awak patut belajar
selok-belok dunia daripada saya.

484
00:25:28,777 --> 00:25:30,779
Awak hanya tahu bekerja sahaja.

485
00:25:33,365 --> 00:25:35,867
Awak tahu tentang ini?
Sekarang ada banyak.

486
00:25:37,577 --> 00:25:39,329
"Pinjaman khas COVID-19."

487
00:25:40,163 --> 00:25:43,833
Dulu saya pernah bekerja
dengan pemiutang untuk cari duit.

488
00:25:43,917 --> 00:25:44,751
Okey.

489
00:25:44,834 --> 00:25:47,587
Orang terdesak lebih mudah jadi mangsa.

490
00:25:47,671 --> 00:25:49,965
Pandemik buat kita lebih terdesak.

491
00:25:52,175 --> 00:25:54,970
Tentu semua lintah darat gembira sekarang.

492
00:25:55,053 --> 00:25:55,887
Kenapa?

493
00:25:55,971 --> 00:25:58,390
Orang pinjam duit untuk bayar sewa,

494
00:25:58,890 --> 00:26:02,519
jadi mereka cuma perlu
ambil kesempatan sepenuhnya.

495
00:26:03,478 --> 00:26:06,565
Mak saya susah hati
disebabkan sewa kafe kami.

496
00:26:07,190 --> 00:26:09,859
Keuntungan tak sampai suku
dari jumlah sebelum ini,

497
00:26:09,943 --> 00:26:11,945
tapi bayaran sewa tetap sama.

498
00:26:13,697 --> 00:26:15,782
Tapi kos tutup kedai lebih tinggi,

499
00:26:15,865 --> 00:26:17,450
jadi kami cuba bertahan.

500
00:26:17,951 --> 00:26:20,537
Kami perlu kembalikan dalam keadaan asal.

501
00:26:22,205 --> 00:26:23,206
Cis.

502
00:26:26,793 --> 00:26:27,627
Nah.

503
00:26:29,796 --> 00:26:32,257
Saya akan belanja awak makanan mahal.

504
00:26:33,300 --> 00:26:34,134
Mata rusuk?

505
00:26:34,217 --> 00:26:36,970
Ada kedai daging yang turut jual barbeku.

506
00:26:37,053 --> 00:26:38,305
Awak tak tipu?

507
00:26:38,388 --> 00:26:40,765
Hei, saya takkan gunakan daging

508
00:26:40,849 --> 00:26:43,018
untuk tipu pegawai atasan saya.

509
00:26:43,101 --> 00:26:44,311
Saya rasa awak tipu.

510
00:26:44,394 --> 00:26:45,395
Awak tak percaya?

511
00:26:45,478 --> 00:26:47,897
Dari tadi awak asyik tipu saya.

512
00:26:47,981 --> 00:26:50,317
Ceh. Saya bergurau.

513
00:26:50,817 --> 00:26:52,319
Okey, saya takkan tipu lagi.

514
00:26:53,862 --> 00:26:54,696
Okey.

515
00:26:55,864 --> 00:26:59,075
Saya minta maaf banyak.

516
00:26:59,159 --> 00:27:02,621
Saya patut bayar bulan ini,

517
00:27:03,121 --> 00:27:04,748
tapi saya tak mampu.

518
00:27:05,498 --> 00:27:09,794
Ya, saya akan usahakan sesuatu
untuk bulan depan.

519
00:27:11,129 --> 00:27:12,213
Saya minta maaf.

520
00:27:14,049 --> 00:27:15,967
- Maaf, saya letak dulu.
- Mak.

521
00:27:16,051 --> 00:27:17,177
Saya telefon esok.

522
00:27:18,136 --> 00:27:19,596
Anak mak!

523
00:27:20,347 --> 00:27:21,931
Aduhai!

524
00:27:23,892 --> 00:27:25,935
Hari ini awak sangat mengagumkan!

525
00:27:26,019 --> 00:27:28,480
- Mak tengok?
- Tentulah!

526
00:27:28,563 --> 00:27:30,857
Para pengulas banyak puji awak.

527
00:27:30,940 --> 00:27:33,777
- Yakah?
- Mereka kata serangan awak sempurna.

528
00:27:33,860 --> 00:27:34,986
Saya patut tonton.

529
00:27:36,154 --> 00:27:37,739
- Mak, sekejap.
- Okey.

530
00:27:37,822 --> 00:27:39,157
Mak bangga.

531
00:27:40,200 --> 00:27:41,326
Nah.

532
00:27:42,202 --> 00:27:43,161
Apa ini?

533
00:27:43,953 --> 00:27:45,997
Duit ganjaran. Bayar sewa kedai.

534
00:27:50,001 --> 00:27:51,836
Mak tak boleh terima.

535
00:27:53,505 --> 00:27:55,423
Saya menang untuk mak.

536
00:27:59,010 --> 00:28:02,389
Kita bayar duit pak cik dulu.

537
00:28:02,472 --> 00:28:03,348
Apa?

538
00:28:04,557 --> 00:28:06,601
Bagaimana awak tahu tentang itu?

539
00:28:06,685 --> 00:28:09,979
Pak cik susah juga.
Kita bayar duit dia dulu.

540
00:28:14,609 --> 00:28:15,568
Okey.

541
00:28:16,653 --> 00:28:19,489
Mak akan bayar duit awak ini
siap dengan faedah.

542
00:28:19,572 --> 00:28:22,575
- Okey.
- Terima kasih.

543
00:28:26,287 --> 00:28:27,414
Mak, jom.

544
00:28:27,497 --> 00:28:28,957
Sejuknya. Jom.

545
00:28:29,999 --> 00:28:31,292
Awak dah makan?

546
00:28:31,376 --> 00:28:32,252
Ya, sudah.

547
00:28:32,335 --> 00:28:33,795
Yakah? Dengan siapa?

548
00:28:34,379 --> 00:28:36,423
Bersama lawan pusingan akhir saya.

549
00:28:37,549 --> 00:28:40,802
Maksud awak, petinju
dengan rambut keriting itu?

550
00:28:40,885 --> 00:28:41,845
Betul.

551
00:28:43,930 --> 00:28:45,056
Mak dah makan?

552
00:28:45,140 --> 00:28:46,516
Mak dah makan.

553
00:29:05,201 --> 00:29:06,035
En. Kim.

554
00:29:06,619 --> 00:29:07,454
Bagaimana?

555
00:29:08,496 --> 00:29:12,834
Betul kata awak. Mereka berhutang
dengan bank atau pengantara bukan bank.

556
00:29:13,585 --> 00:29:16,629
Saya akan jadikan
mereka klien kita minggu depan.

557
00:29:16,713 --> 00:29:17,547
Itu…

558
00:29:18,047 --> 00:29:19,424
Tak boleh minggu ini?

559
00:29:20,258 --> 00:29:22,969
Ahli Dewan Seo bising mahu mereka dihalau.

560
00:29:24,554 --> 00:29:27,724
- Saya akan uruskan.
- Okey. Uruskan dengan segera.

561
00:29:28,349 --> 00:29:30,268
Unit jualan paling penting.

562
00:29:31,060 --> 00:29:31,895
Ya.

563
00:29:36,483 --> 00:29:37,567
Beom.

564
00:29:39,652 --> 00:29:40,570
Siap sedia.

565
00:30:00,215 --> 00:30:03,301
Saya Pengurus Yoo In-yeong
dari Smile Capital.

566
00:30:03,885 --> 00:30:04,761
Syarikat kami

567
00:30:04,844 --> 00:30:07,806
terima sijil kecemerlangan
daripada kerajaan.

568
00:30:07,889 --> 00:30:11,643
Jika encik ada masa,
boleh kita berbual sekejap?

569
00:30:11,726 --> 00:30:12,727
Boleh.

570
00:30:12,811 --> 00:30:15,897
Kebelakangan ini,
tak ramai pelanggan, bukan?

571
00:30:17,398 --> 00:30:18,316
Ya.

572
00:30:18,399 --> 00:30:21,152
Pinjaman encik berjumlah
40 juta won, bukan?

573
00:30:21,778 --> 00:30:22,612
Betul.

574
00:30:22,695 --> 00:30:24,072
Tandatangan di sini

575
00:30:24,155 --> 00:30:27,075
dan kami akan langsaikan
hutang awak hari ini.

576
00:30:27,158 --> 00:30:29,536
Berbanding kadar faedah bank 7 peratus,

577
00:30:29,619 --> 00:30:31,412
kami tawarkan 5 peratus.

578
00:30:31,496 --> 00:30:34,290
Kalau begitu, bukankah awak akan rugi?

579
00:30:34,374 --> 00:30:35,416
Betul.

580
00:30:35,500 --> 00:30:37,627
Tapi pihak kerajaan telah memulakan

581
00:30:37,710 --> 00:30:40,797
program bantuan khas
bagi membantu para peniaga kecil

582
00:30:40,880 --> 00:30:43,091
yang terkesan akibat pandemik ini.

583
00:30:43,174 --> 00:30:47,136
Kami menang bidaan pakej bantuan
dan mampu tawarkan kadar rendah.

584
00:30:47,220 --> 00:30:50,098
Kadar faedah 2 peratus bukannya kecil.

585
00:30:50,723 --> 00:30:53,768
Dalam waktu begini,
kita kena bertahan untuk menang.

586
00:30:55,603 --> 00:30:58,189
Pandemik? Ia pasti akan berakhir.

587
00:30:58,731 --> 00:31:02,777
Kami ingin hulurkan sedikit bantuan
agar awak boleh terus berniaga.

588
00:31:05,363 --> 00:31:07,031
Bukan sahaja pihak kami,

589
00:31:07,115 --> 00:31:09,242
tapi ia bagus untuk pak cik juga.

590
00:31:12,370 --> 00:31:13,413
Terima kasih.

591
00:31:13,496 --> 00:31:14,831
Terima kasih.

592
00:31:14,914 --> 00:31:16,332
SMILE CAPITAL
YOON SO-YEON

593
00:31:20,795 --> 00:31:22,881
GIM TINJU SPARK

594
00:31:32,557 --> 00:31:33,516
Eh?

595
00:31:33,600 --> 00:31:35,018
PENUTUPAN SEMENTARA WAKTU
AKIBAT JANGKITAN COVID-19

596
00:31:35,101 --> 00:31:36,269
Malam semalam,

597
00:31:36,352 --> 00:31:38,897
kami makan ayam goreng di gim.

598
00:31:38,980 --> 00:31:41,232
Ada seorang disahkan positif.

599
00:31:42,066 --> 00:31:44,152
Patutkah saya buat ujian juga?

600
00:31:44,652 --> 00:31:45,486
Tak perlu.

601
00:31:46,070 --> 00:31:50,074
Perlawanan awak semalam,
kenapa awak dah ke gim semula?

602
00:31:50,158 --> 00:31:52,535
- Untuk bersenam.
- Gun-woo.

603
00:31:53,202 --> 00:31:54,329
Rehatlah seminggu.

604
00:31:54,954 --> 00:31:56,205
Untuk buat apa?

605
00:31:56,289 --> 00:31:58,499
Jika kena buat sesuatu, itu bukan rehat.

606
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:00,752
Tak perlu buat apa-apa.

607
00:32:01,502 --> 00:32:02,337
Baiklah.

608
00:32:12,847 --> 00:32:15,183
GU-NOO

609
00:32:22,941 --> 00:32:24,525
Helo? Buat apa?

610
00:32:26,319 --> 00:32:27,528
Tidur.

611
00:32:27,612 --> 00:32:28,655
Apa?

612
00:32:28,738 --> 00:32:30,031
Tidur.

613
00:32:31,115 --> 00:32:32,241
Saya tak dengar.

614
00:32:32,325 --> 00:32:33,576
Saya tidur.

615
00:32:33,660 --> 00:32:35,745
Saya tidur.

616
00:32:36,621 --> 00:32:38,081
Nak bersenam?

617
00:32:38,581 --> 00:32:40,750
Tak nak.

618
00:32:40,833 --> 00:32:42,126
Saya bosan.

619
00:32:42,210 --> 00:32:45,380
Awal pagi lagi dah merengek.

620
00:32:45,964 --> 00:32:47,382
Jom melepak.

621
00:32:49,926 --> 00:32:52,720
Saya beri alamat saya. Datanglah.

622
00:32:53,596 --> 00:32:54,555
Okey.

623
00:33:10,863 --> 00:33:12,031
Jahanam!

624
00:33:13,866 --> 00:33:15,868
Berhenti! Bedebah!

625
00:34:01,581 --> 00:34:03,416
Encik tak apa-apa?

626
00:34:04,125 --> 00:34:05,251
Tunggu…

627
00:34:32,695 --> 00:34:33,529
Apa hal?

628
00:34:35,114 --> 00:34:36,074
Kenapa kejar?

629
00:34:37,116 --> 00:34:38,242
Siapa hantar awak?

630
00:34:40,369 --> 00:34:42,538
Saya cuma nak membantu.

631
00:34:42,622 --> 00:34:43,456
Apa?

632
00:34:44,123 --> 00:34:44,957
Siapa?

633
00:34:46,209 --> 00:34:49,796
Saya sangka lelaki tadi kena kejar…

634
00:34:50,713 --> 00:34:52,840
- Celaka!
- Eh?

635
00:34:52,924 --> 00:34:54,717
Dia berlakon.

636
00:34:54,801 --> 00:34:56,636
- Apa?
- Jangan menyibuk.

637
00:34:56,719 --> 00:34:59,347
- Okey.
- Menyusahkan betul.

638
00:35:05,103 --> 00:35:05,937
Wah…

639
00:35:35,174 --> 00:35:36,092
Ada apa?

640
00:35:36,175 --> 00:35:40,138
Pembedahan Mi-yeon berjalan
dengan lancar semalam.

641
00:35:40,221 --> 00:35:42,390
Yakah? Bagaimana keadaan dia?

642
00:35:42,974 --> 00:35:46,018
Baik. Dia semakin pulih.

643
00:35:48,271 --> 00:35:49,856
Semuanya atas jasa awak.

644
00:35:50,565 --> 00:35:52,608
Tanpa bantuan awak,

645
00:35:53,109 --> 00:35:56,237
Mi-yeon mungkin tak dapat diselamatkan.

646
00:35:59,323 --> 00:36:00,158
Ini.

647
00:36:02,034 --> 00:36:05,121
Suami saya baru diterima
bekerja di syarikat besar

648
00:36:05,204 --> 00:36:07,373
dan dia terima bayaran.

649
00:36:08,916 --> 00:36:11,669
Saya datang sebaik sahaja duit diterima

650
00:36:11,752 --> 00:36:14,130
sebab nak lunaskan pinjaman awak dulu.

651
00:36:17,592 --> 00:36:19,218
Awak boleh bayar kemudian.

652
00:36:20,761 --> 00:36:22,263
Utamakan bayaran lain.

653
00:36:22,847 --> 00:36:26,475
Tak mengapa. Tolong ambil duit ini.

654
00:36:27,268 --> 00:36:29,437
Barulah lega hati saya.

655
00:36:32,398 --> 00:36:33,941
Terima kasih.

656
00:36:35,818 --> 00:36:38,362
Terima kasih banyak.

657
00:36:41,073 --> 00:36:42,241
Terima kasih.

658
00:36:58,799 --> 00:37:00,927
IBU MI-YEON, 14 APRIL 2018
20 JUTA WON

659
00:37:06,724 --> 00:37:08,768
KEDAI ANTIK KOREA

660
00:37:32,792 --> 00:37:35,670
Saya jumpa Yang Jae-myeong,
tapi kononnya dia pokai.

661
00:37:36,712 --> 00:37:37,588
Saya ambil ini.

662
00:37:42,051 --> 00:37:43,511
Nilainya lebih 20 juta.

663
00:37:44,011 --> 00:37:45,054
Jadi?

664
00:37:46,055 --> 00:37:48,057
Dia cuma pinjam sepuluh juta won.

665
00:37:49,058 --> 00:37:50,101
Kita kaut faedah.

666
00:37:56,148 --> 00:37:57,191
Awak cedera?

667
00:37:57,275 --> 00:37:59,735
Tak guna. Saya bergaduh dengan dia.

668
00:38:00,736 --> 00:38:01,570
Oh, ya.

669
00:38:02,071 --> 00:38:04,448
Saya baru ingat. Kita perlu berbincang.

670
00:38:04,532 --> 00:38:05,783
Makan ddeok.

671
00:38:06,701 --> 00:38:09,203
Jangan gunakan ddeok untuk mengelak.

672
00:38:11,706 --> 00:38:12,999
Sampai bila lagi?

673
00:38:14,417 --> 00:38:15,251
Apa?

674
00:38:17,586 --> 00:38:19,213
Pinjaman tanpa faedah.

675
00:38:19,297 --> 00:38:20,840
Ia tak menguntungkan.

676
00:38:21,465 --> 00:38:22,633
Apa maksud awak?

677
00:38:22,717 --> 00:38:25,845
Datuk sentiasa bayar awak
komisen 30 peratus.

678
00:38:25,928 --> 00:38:28,097
Saya maksudkan datuk.

679
00:38:31,934 --> 00:38:33,644
Awak kenal ibu Mi-yeon, kan?

680
00:38:34,770 --> 00:38:35,771
Kenapa?

681
00:38:35,855 --> 00:38:39,358
Dia datang dan buat bayaran tunai.

682
00:38:41,319 --> 00:38:42,486
Itu pula faedahnya?

683
00:38:44,613 --> 00:38:45,531
Hyeon-ju.

684
00:38:46,240 --> 00:38:48,909
Anak dia pulih
kerana dibedah tepat pada masanya.

685
00:38:48,993 --> 00:38:50,661
Dengan pinjaman ini,

686
00:38:50,745 --> 00:38:53,664
mereka tak perlu
gadaikan rumah untuk pinjaman.

687
00:38:53,748 --> 00:38:57,168
Mereka masih ada rumah
untuk sambut anak mereka.

688
00:38:58,586 --> 00:39:00,504
Kita selamatkan sebuah keluarga.

689
00:39:01,339 --> 00:39:04,216
Ini kadar faedah
paling berharga dalam dunia.

690
00:39:07,845 --> 00:39:10,014
Apa-apa pun, ketika mencari Yang

691
00:39:10,097 --> 00:39:12,016
saya dapat tahu tentang sesuatu.

692
00:39:12,892 --> 00:39:16,187
Yang dan konco dia
menyamar jadi gelandangan

693
00:39:16,687 --> 00:39:19,357
dan curi ID gelandangan
untuk buat pinjaman.

694
00:39:19,440 --> 00:39:21,067
Siapa mereka?

695
00:39:21,150 --> 00:39:23,277
Rakan-rakan banduan Yang Jae-myeong.

696
00:39:23,361 --> 00:39:24,403
Samseng.

697
00:39:24,487 --> 00:39:26,447
Awak tahu dan awak pergi sendirian?

698
00:39:27,406 --> 00:39:28,991
Datuk nak pergi sama?

699
00:39:29,658 --> 00:39:32,078
Apa-apa pun, saya akan terus siasat.

700
00:39:32,578 --> 00:39:34,080
Tentu ada sesuatu.

701
00:39:34,163 --> 00:39:35,998
Jangan bahayakan diri.

702
00:39:36,707 --> 00:39:37,541
Baiklah.

703
00:39:47,426 --> 00:39:50,471
PRESIDEN MOON GWANG-MU

704
00:39:52,765 --> 00:39:53,599
Helo.

705
00:39:54,183 --> 00:39:56,060
Hei, awak sibuk?

706
00:39:56,560 --> 00:39:57,770
Tak, saya tak sibuk.

707
00:39:57,853 --> 00:40:00,856
Saya perlukan bantuan
untuk cari seseorang.

708
00:40:00,940 --> 00:40:01,899
Baiklah. Tunggu.

709
00:40:03,859 --> 00:40:04,819
Saya dah sedia.

710
00:40:05,986 --> 00:40:06,904
"Baik.

711
00:40:08,197 --> 00:40:09,657
Pengawal berpengalaman,

712
00:40:10,741 --> 00:40:13,411
lebih bagus jika tahu
selok-belok pinjaman."

713
00:40:16,330 --> 00:40:17,748
Baiklah.

714
00:40:18,249 --> 00:40:20,835
Saya akan cari calon secepat mungkin.

715
00:40:21,460 --> 00:40:22,753
Okey, terima kasih.

716
00:40:22,837 --> 00:40:25,214
Baiklah. Tabik!

717
00:40:26,715 --> 00:40:29,051
Mayweather paling unggul.

718
00:40:29,635 --> 00:40:32,471
Tapi dia tak macam petinju,
tapi ahli perniagaan.

719
00:40:32,555 --> 00:40:34,807
Betul. Dia memang cari duit,

720
00:40:34,890 --> 00:40:36,434
tapi dia juga hebat.

721
00:40:36,517 --> 00:40:38,727
Tentu dia dibayar beratus bilion won.

722
00:40:39,562 --> 00:40:40,771
Awak pentingkan duit?

723
00:40:41,939 --> 00:40:43,357
Ada yang lebih penting?

724
00:40:44,066 --> 00:40:45,192
Jiwa petinju.

725
00:40:48,320 --> 00:40:49,196
Kenapa?

726
00:40:51,866 --> 00:40:53,242
Kenapa?

727
00:40:55,995 --> 00:40:57,997
- Kenapa?
- Tiada apa-apa. Maaf.

728
00:40:58,080 --> 00:40:59,540
Aduhai.

729
00:41:00,082 --> 00:41:04,462
Saya tergamam melihat awak
berubah serius secara tiba-tiba.

730
00:41:04,962 --> 00:41:06,922
Ceritalah. Jiwa petinju.

731
00:41:09,508 --> 00:41:11,927
Bagi saya, Manny Pacquiao yang terunggul.

732
00:41:12,011 --> 00:41:13,012
Pa!

733
00:41:13,512 --> 00:41:15,306
Pa, Pacquiao!

734
00:41:15,389 --> 00:41:16,765
Dengarlah dulu.

735
00:41:16,849 --> 00:41:18,642
Saya tak pernah menyampuk.

736
00:41:19,393 --> 00:41:21,812
Maaf, tuan. Saya takkan menyampuk.

737
00:41:22,730 --> 00:41:26,942
Semangat Pacquiao sangat mengagumkan.
Dia tak putus asa.

738
00:41:27,026 --> 00:41:27,943
Saya setuju.

739
00:41:28,027 --> 00:41:30,321
Tapi Mayweather jauh lebih kaya.

740
00:41:30,821 --> 00:41:34,658
Tapi tentu lebih ramai
yang ingin jadi petinju kerana Pacquiao.

741
00:41:34,742 --> 00:41:36,076
Saya juga.

742
00:41:37,620 --> 00:41:40,539
Woo-jin, ini impian saya.

743
00:41:40,623 --> 00:41:43,667
Orang yang buktikan
dengan kesungguhan dan semangat,

744
00:41:44,210 --> 00:41:46,212
impian boleh jadi kenyataan.

745
00:41:46,295 --> 00:41:47,796
Kuatnya angin hari ini.

746
00:41:47,880 --> 00:41:50,007
Itulah jiwa sebenar seorang petinju

747
00:41:50,090 --> 00:41:52,259
dan harapan yang patut kita berikan

748
00:41:52,343 --> 00:41:54,470
kepada para penonton kita.

749
00:41:54,553 --> 00:41:56,138
- Jiwa…
- Hei, dah masak.

750
00:41:56,222 --> 00:41:57,181
Jom makan.

751
00:41:59,350 --> 00:42:00,184
Nah.

752
00:42:05,689 --> 00:42:07,399
- Sedap?
- Ya, sedap.

753
00:42:08,609 --> 00:42:10,819
Apa pekerjaan awak?

754
00:42:10,903 --> 00:42:11,737
Dulu

755
00:42:12,446 --> 00:42:15,366
saya ajar budak-budak
di tadika kawan saya.

756
00:42:15,449 --> 00:42:16,534
Cikgu sukan.

757
00:42:17,034 --> 00:42:18,536
Tak sesuai dengan awak.

758
00:42:18,619 --> 00:42:22,414
Apa maksud awak?
Budak-budak suka dengan saya.

759
00:42:22,498 --> 00:42:24,959
Pagi saya mengajar, petang saya berlatih.

760
00:42:25,042 --> 00:42:27,920
Tapi saya tak bekerja
sejak tadika ditutup.

761
00:42:30,381 --> 00:42:32,633
Apa kata ikut saya buat penghantaran?

762
00:42:32,716 --> 00:42:34,176
Kerja ini sangat sibuk.

763
00:42:35,177 --> 00:42:36,637
- Bayarannya bagus?
- Ya.

764
00:42:36,720 --> 00:42:38,305
Jika kita tekad,

765
00:42:38,389 --> 00:42:40,766
boleh dapat bayaran 200,000 won sehari.

766
00:42:40,849 --> 00:42:41,725
Yakah?

767
00:42:41,809 --> 00:42:43,727
Ya, dan ia senaman yang bagus.

768
00:42:43,811 --> 00:42:47,147
Bagus untuk keseimbangan sebab guna otot
yang tak digunakan dalam tinju.

769
00:42:47,231 --> 00:42:49,441
Ini bak menyelam sambil minum air.

770
00:42:49,525 --> 00:42:51,569
- Lebih daripada itu.
- Kenapa?

771
00:42:52,152 --> 00:42:54,572
Dapat duit, bagus untuk kardio
dan keseimbangan.

772
00:42:54,655 --> 00:42:57,157
Hei, itu dikira sebagai satu.

773
00:42:57,241 --> 00:42:58,993
Tak, ia berbeza.

774
00:42:59,076 --> 00:43:00,244
Aduhai.

775
