Beom.

801
00:44:29,333 --> 00:44:31,669
Saya tahu awak boleh,
tapi empat juta untuk gagal.

802
00:44:33,837 --> 00:44:36,340
- Kang In-beom!
- Mulakan!

803
00:44:36,423 --> 00:44:39,134
- Kang In-beom!
- Kang In-beom!

804
00:44:39,218 --> 00:44:41,178
- Tunjukkan!
- Kang In-beom!

805
00:44:43,097 --> 00:44:43,972
