810
00:44:52,815 --> 00:44:54,650
TUAN DATUK BANDAR

811
00:44:56,902 --> 00:44:58,570
Diam!

812
00:45:05,119 --> 00:45:06,120
Helo, tuan.

813
00:45:08,580 --> 00:45:09,415
Ya.

814
00:45:12,626 --> 00:45:13,627
Ya.

815
00:45:18,173 --> 00:45:19,007
Baiklah.

816
00:45:20,175 --> 00:45:21,385
Saya faham.

817
00:45:21,468 --> 00:45:22,761
Saya akan maklumkan.

818
00:45:23,887 --> 00:45:25,055
Selamat malam.

819
00:45:29,601 --> 00:45:31,770
Datuk bandar setuju untuk sokong

820
00:45:33,021 --> 00:45:34,690
projek kasino awak.

821
00:45:43,240 --> 00:45:44,241
Saya sediakan

822
00:45:44,992 --> 00:45:46,618
sebuah hadiah tak seberapa

823
00:45:46,702 --> 00:45:49,288
bersempena hari lahir awak.

824
00:45:54,543 --> 00:45:55,377
Bukalah.

825
00:46:02,468 --> 00:46:03,594
Emas 3.7 kilogram.

826
00:46:04,678 --> 00:46:05,554
En. Park.

827
00:46:06,138 --> 00:46:09,683
Kura-kura itu sangat bersih
dan awak tak perlu risau.

828
00:46:10,768 --> 00:46:12,269
Hadiah ini saya sediakan

829
00:46:12,352 --> 00:46:15,272
dengan harapan
agar hubungan kita berterusan.

830
00:46:15,355 --> 00:46:18,275
Saya berbesar hati jika awak terima.

831
00:46:27,493 --> 00:46:29,870
Awak perlu pergi lebih jauh.

832
00:46:31,371 --> 00:46:33,415
Saya tahu awak bercita-cita besar.

833
